From: Chao Yu <chao@kernel.org>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 21:35:42 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] f2fs: fix to do sanity check on dcc->discard_cmd_cnt
 conditionally
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 7.0.2
Git-commit: 6af249c996f7d73a3435f9e577956fa259347d18

commit 6af249c996f7d73a3435f9e577956fa259347d18 upstream.

